      • getCorrectionInfo

        public int getCorrectionInfo()
        The correction information
        Returns:
        • 0 data found and stable
        • -1 invalid (value not available)
        • -2 unavailable data too far in the past
        • -3 unavailable
        • -4: too soon (early warmup)
        • -5: Almost stable. Device disconnected in the last 1 min
        • -6: after a short disconnection, data before disconnection are not corrected for warmup
